snippet.title: Fireside Chat with Jeff Bezos | Shah Rukh Khan, Zoya Akhtar | Amazon Prime Video
snippet.description:
Jeff Bezos – CEO and President, Amazon, gets candid in a fireside chat with Actor Shah Rukh Khan and Filmmaker Zoya Akhtar at the event marking his Maiden Mumbai visit and 3 years of Amazon Prime Video in India.
